FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://iot-bath-light-sensor.herokuapp.com/webapi

# bath-light-sensor

This is API enables the user to check whether a bathroom light in a given house and room is on or not. 

## Single Light Status [/status/house/house_id/room/room_id]

### Single Light Status[GET]

Returns the status of the light in a single bathroom.

+ Parameters
    + house_id (number) - ID of the given house
    + room_id (number) - ID of the given room
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "house_id": "3",
            "room_id": "5",
            "is_light_on": "true",
            "light_switch_time": "2016-06-11T22:13:06.460Z"
        }

