## Single Room History [/history/house/house_id/room/room_id]

### Room History[GET]

Returns the history of light switches in a single bathroom.

+ Parameters
    + house_id (number) - ID of the given house
    + room_id (number) - ID of the given room

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "house_id": "4",
            "room_id": "1",
            "history":
                [
                    {
                        "light_on": "true",
                        "light_switch_time": "2016-06-11T22:15:07.220Z"
                    },
                    {
                        "light_on": "false",
                        "light_switch_time": "2016-06-11T22:15:34.513Z"
                    },
                    {
                        "light_on": "true",
                        "light_switch_time": "2016-06-11T22:17:23.410Z"
                    }
                ]
        }
        
